ce:section.ce:para:
The catalytic reaction of TMB was measured by SERS spectroscopy under the same conditions as described above. Kinetic experiments were carried out to study the kinetics of the nanozyme by adding different volumes of TMB (5 mM). The SERS intensity (1336 cm−1) was measured at 5 s intervals (within 60 s). The SERS steady-state kinetic parameters (Km
                         and Vmax
                        ) were also calculated from the Lineweaver-Burk plot of the Michaelis-Menten equation double inverse.
